@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to the Budget Tracker</h1>
    <p>
        BudgetingApp is a personal finance management tool designed to help users track income, 
        categorize expenses, and monitor financial trends over time.
    </p>
    <p>
        The application provides a centralized dashboard for managing financial activity, allowing users to 
        record transactions, organize spending categories, and visualize monthly budgeting performance.
    </p>
    <p>
        Built using ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, and SQL Server, the system emphasizes structured 
        financial tracking, secure user authentication, and responsive web design.
    </p>
</div>
